or use this 
var regex = /^(EJWIN10)(1\d{5})$/i;
With /i  Matches EJWIN10, ejwin10, EjWiN10 , there is no need to conert in uppercase or lower case 
Without /i EJWIN10	Only matches the exact string EJWIN10. thatwhy you need to turn to lowercase
